data.description: Step into your dream home nestled in the heart of Cibolo! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath residence boasts a spacious, open floor plan and impressive architectural features. As you enter, marvel at the soaring ceilings and grand foyer leading to a formal living room adjacent to an elegant staircase. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, 42" cabinets, and multiple dining areas, including a formal dining room and cozy breakfast nook. The first floor hosts the luxurious Owner's suite, offering high ceilings, a garden tub, separate shower, a generous closet, and double vanity. Upstairs, a Jack and Jill bathroom connects two sizable bedrooms, while the third and fourth bedrooms enjoy direct access to another bathroom. A versatile family/game/flex room adds to the home's appeal. Above the garage, discover a finished storage area spanning an impressive 421 Sq Ft, offering limitless possibilities as a man or she cave, office, or creative space (please note: no heating or AC in this area). Outdoors, relax by the pool and hot tub, entertain on the covered patio, or bask in the sun on the deck. Additionally, a new roof installed in 2022 provides added peace of mind. Situated in a community with a park, pool, and walking trails, this home is part of the highly regarded SCUCISD. Its proximity to highways and shopping centers combines luxury living with convenience. Welcome to your new haven!
